</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/swim-deep">Swim Deep</a>在他们的新专辑之前以“第一首歌”的形式回归了最新单曲 - 听下面的歌曲。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="61" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/swim-deep-interview-emerald-classics-2559946"><b>在经历了荒野岁月之后，深入游泳寻找焦点：“我们需要踢屁股”</b></a></li></ul><p>伯明翰乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/swim-deep-announce-new-album-theres-a-big-star-outside-produced-by-bill-ryder-jones-3590752">于二月份宣布了他们的第四张专辑“There&#39;s a Big Star Outside”</a> ，并分享了其主打单曲“How Many Love Songs Have Died in Vegas？”同时。</p><p>现在，最新的品尝者已经揭晓。在这里观看“第一首歌”的视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="游得深 - 第一首歌" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XpJzL_iq8bE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>主唱奥斯汀·威廉姆斯 (Austin Williams) 分享道：“这首歌是在卡文 (Cavan) 沉迷于 Mogwai 之后创作的，我对自己制作的这首琶音循环非常着迷。这是其中一首刚刚出现的歌曲，基线自然而然地出现了。”</p><p> “我想要一首有意义的歌曲的驱动力。歌词围绕着我儿时的梦想，与两个父母、两辆车、一只猫、一个“核心”家庭过着郊区的生活。但后来想想，我所拥有的实际上是我的造就，而且它实际上很酷。它给了我原始的爱、自由、逃避现实，我不会改变它，因为雷诺风景是世界上一个盛大的暑假。”</p><p>这张包含 10 首曲目的专辑将于 6 月 7 日通过 Submarine Cat Records 发行（<a href="https://subc.at/BigStarOutside" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。继 2019 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/swim-deep-emerald-classics-album-review-2553884">“Emerald Classics”</a>之后，即将推出的系列由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bill-ryder-jones">Bill Ryder-Jones</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">《Yard Act》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wytches">《The Wytches</a> 》）制作。 <br /><b></b></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4_JpamNZFh/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565